Because the notes accumulate over time, I build compound interest on my thinking. Today's half-formed thought becomes next month's breakthrough connection.

This applies to both the human Zettelkasten and the AI context layer. A well-maintained context layer gets more valuable over time. Every interaction, every meeting, every decision enriches it. The longer I invest, the wider the gap between my AI capability and someone starting from scratch.

Vendor memory resets when I move. My context layer compounds.
